This page on SteamDB lists all video games tagged as 'eSports' on the Steam platform. eSports, or electronic sports, refers to organized, multiplayer competitive gaming. These games often have large communities of dedicated players and regular tournaments with substantial prizes. The 'eSports' tag on Steam helps identify titles that are popular in the competitive gaming scene. Games tagged as eSports may have professional leagues, sponsored teams, and regular events, attracting both amateur and professional players. The page is automatically updated to reflect the latest additions, removal, or changes to games tagged as eSports on Steam.
